{"tid":1008222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩萬粉絲戀上High Tea　午後幸福時光","createTime":"2019-02-04T10:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T11:55:36.000Z","uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3037b69701f13e54065b04b3c3b26b3e27a37d11","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj01p.jpg&h=e7f97dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和暖的午後，喝一口熱茶，吃一件英式鬆餅，與幾個友好坐在優美的餐廳中說說笑笑，幸福，對女生來說就是這樣簡單。由兩萬多人組成的社交專頁High Tea Club，約定每個月到香港不同地方享受下午茶，大家原本各不相識卻志同道合，或許在過程中沒有很大的得着，但每次聚會總會帶着美好的心情離開。 <br />\n<br />\n記者：周藍 <br />\n攝影：林栢鈞、陳國良"},{"pid":"c46219ce9d26021d801cf73f81efec4aa3f8bf52","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj09p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj09p.jpg&h=5c21dfe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHigh Tea Club清一色女生 <br />\n每月茶敍分享心得 <br />\n下午茶團長Fiona29歲 <br />\n職業：社交媒體 <br />\nHigh Tea經驗：5年 <br />\nFacebook上一個粉絲專頁High Tea Club，半年已吸引兩萬多粉絲，網主Fiona更應網友要求每個月定期舉辦下午茶活動，數月間由開頭八位參加者增至50人，每次名額都很快爆滿！「這個Page純粹為分享下午茶的喜悅和心得，估唔到咁受歡迎！」起初辦活動時Fiona很害怕，因全部參加者都是陌生人。「還記得我當時預先想好一些話題，希望氣氛熱鬧一點，但很高興她們都非常投契又主動，嘻嘻哈哈的便度過一個愉快下午。」有趣的是，Fiona從沒有規限參加者資格，但幾乎是清一色女生，個個都斯斯文文，更不乏專業人士。「每次聚會都認識到很多新朋友，有的對下午茶文化很執着，連對沖茶的水溫都很講究，有的只為結交志同道合的朋友。」經了解後，我發現她們不只是喜歡這個文化，背後還有很多故事。"},{"pid":"a34712fd8128c52039101583433c0a8d2b5d9656","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj04p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj04p.jpg&h=ad6e38b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白衣天使失戀　愛上烘焙服 <br />\n網絡烘焙紅人KaKa24歲 <br />\n職業：護士 <br />\nHigh Tea經驗：2年 <br />\n「每天早上把我弄醒的不是鬧鐘，而是夢想。」這是眼裏都泛着滿腔熱誠的KaKa的格言。成為護士是父母心願，長大後才發現自己想成為餅師，轉捩點全因一次下午茶旅程。剛失戀的KaKa獨自到台灣旅行，在心情十分低落時，找了一家甜品小店吃下午茶，一口芝士蛋糕，便感動得快哭出來，原來用心做的甜點可燃亮別人的生命。回港後她加入High Tea Club，到處品嚐下午茶；之後更嘗試自己親手做，起初做了些曲奇餅放在父母經營的茶餐廳擺賣，之後便設計一些卡通角色的杯子蛋糕，還迅速在網上火紅起來。在網上建立自家甜品店兩年的Kaka，決心明年底辭去護士工作到台灣學烘焙，努力圓夢。「或許是當護士期間感受到生命無常，應該好好活在當下，做自己喜歡做的事。」"},{"pid":"d1d2316322d160874fcb6fa166424c271fffcbdf","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj08p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj08p.jpg&h=4b5acba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為甜品瘋狂　為下午茶轉行 <br />\n下午茶設計師Coty31歲 <br />\n職業：餐廳市場部 <br />\nHigh Tea經驗：7年 <br />\n「別人買蛋糕是一件件買，我卻是一磅磅買！一吃便是半磅，連同坐的友人都側目！」從吃甜品的份量，可看得出瘋狂程度，未算去得盡？她還為下午茶而轉行。本身是公關的Coty得知公司旗下有間意大利餐廳正在聘請市場推廣員，她二話不說便舉手請纓。初報到已極力向餐廳提議推出下午茶餐單，經多次修改計劃後主管終於接納，由揀選餐具到茶點款式，全都有份參與。「希望能將自己難忘的下午茶經驗轉化成工作的一部份，將快樂傳遞開去。」"},{"pid":"76917a949b1493cbb7f4957c0cb9655f0012d4ad","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj07pnew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj07pnew.jpg&h=e7b23423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDress Code：時尚休閒 <br />\n資深達人Hilary27歲 <br />\n職業：銀行 <br />\nHigh Tea經驗：10年 <br />\n讀中學時已渴望到酒店High Tea，為去一次曾和幾個同學儲足一個月零用錢。因太喜愛精緻的茶點，現在副業做杯子蛋糕，今次便特意做了粉色系立體花杯子蛋糕送給到場的姊妹。"},{"pid":"92f15b3a56041f2ccb5dab565a6b7a9bb80a2634","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj06pnew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj06pnew.jpg&h=7c17784c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n襯到一絕Cardy25歲 <br />\n職業：化妝師 <br />\nHigh Tea經驗：4年 <br />\n「男仔從來唔明女仔食甜品點解食咁耐。」對她來說中午12至6點都是High Tea時間，而且每次都會配合主題悉心打扮，田園餐廳會穿碎花裙，高貴酒店會穿淑女長裙，視扮靚為快樂。"},{"pid":"9a3b5d8f10683cd217a5e3282c5b7db07a3a7859","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj05pnew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj05pnew.jpg&h=0b89aabc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相機先食Jacko31歲 <br />\n職業：廣告營業員 <br />\nHigh Tea經驗：3年 <br />\n丈夫是攝影師，自己也愛攝影，下午茶時會逐一給精緻茶點拍照，她笑說朋友有時會鼓譟問「食得未啊？」她說暫未有一間環境讓她滿意，因出名的場地通常多人排隊，未食已影響心情。"},{"pid":"30ad043b0ac753bf51099dc6790e9c2d2e0bdae6","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj03pnew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj03pnew.jpg&h=e4b40f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n充電Break Time項項25歲 <br />\n職業：文員 <br />\nHigh Tea經驗：2年 <br />\n兩年前來港讀書才認識下午茶文化，喝下午茶像是Break Time，讓自己充充電。香港與中國的下午茶文化分別很大，內地有人會穿拖鞋到酒店High Tea，大部份人都匆匆忙忙吃完就走。"},{"pid":"bbb13ee467583f130fdaa9dff57e6ba19c67bcc5","tid":1008222,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20131126/large/26fj02pnew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20131126%2Flarge%2F26fj02pnew.jpg&h=7f114333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午茶日本通Chloe31歲 <br />\n職業：日語老師 <br />\nHigh Tea經驗：7年 <br />\n「喝下午茶是享受寧靜一刻，我最喜歡到日本銀座青山的Cafe High Tea，當地人從不高談闊論，很優雅斯文。」"},{"pid":"b5735e3a553fa2696bc0cfa59cb0754da73c3a90","tid":1008222,"uid":35228,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"唔知點解<br />\n食high tea冇咩問題<br />\n但個畫面好bitch<br />\nBitch在係充滿是非話題既聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4f5a61cd151aa219a98a5b92d2931c1b317ead","tid":1008222,"uid":26953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"會窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba4a68d60cc5a62c3ffe8b934088fabdecd0d40","tid":1008222,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"而家八個入面都搵唔一件靚女架咩?"},{"pid":"2b36fd18f246ae0fba822c7e2e3161a1c27b5ff0","tid":1008222,"uid":49549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"正宗既英國人係唔會HIGH TEA"},{"pid":"36393536f9af3f757ccaca40f9c7973fd3b1f49f","tid":1008222,"uid":52122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:37:22.000Z","msg":"一班八婆"},{"pid":"403d543714b3e3d158b4757fa5cf222e3808798a","tid":1008222,"uid":55941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:37:31.000Z","msg":"成件事肯定八婆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a860d86b7d87e5133a41c6ee86343682adca751d","tid":1008222,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"2013年 結哂婚未?"},{"pid":"0c9eecfecf3e724ea960a7839bdd54204274df73","tid":1008222,"uid":229789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5735e3a553fa2696bc0cfa59cb0754da73c3a90","tid":1008222,"uid":35228,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"唔知點解<br />\n食high tea冇咩問題<br />\n但個畫面好bitch<br />\nBitch在係充滿是非話題既聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"仲要扮哂蟹咁講：oh really 真係ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9832ef4e16e2025eb52b124373fd400283ec53b","tid":1008222,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"物以類聚"},{"pid":"9b02d6362ecf6b07c87d2350574bd57866802118","tid":1008222,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:44:47.000Z","msg":"hilary ok"},{"pid":"9e019beed06cd40c5339502b975cc259a2d0df98","tid":1008222,"uid":159392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c9eecfecf3e724ea960a7839bdd54204274df73","tid":1008222,"uid":229789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5735e3a553fa2696bc0cfa59cb0754da73c3a90","tid":1008222,"uid":35228,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:31:34.000Z","msg":"唔知點解<br />\n食high tea冇咩問題<br />\n但個畫面好bitch<br />\nBitch在係充滿是非話題既聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"仲要扮哂蟹咁講：oh really 真係ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"Oh 賣 guardddddd"},{"pid":"8c58e41ba7afb22701c6139a19f69bf41daa0cf4","tid":1008222,"uid":173050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b36fd18f246ae0fba822c7e2e3161a1c27b5ff0","tid":1008222,"uid":49549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"正宗既英國人係唔會HIGH TEA"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"一班high tea afternoon tea都未識分嘅港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc61f41ce025522728b93019f013fcc67a985898","tid":1008222,"uid":197194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"話說佢地揀錯地方喎，high tea 應該唔會係呢d地方搞架喎"}]}